These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, climbing, cycling, rugby
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat, pony, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the owner of the cat is the fan of techno##1
2. the owner of the pony is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is rugby##2
3. the owner of the cat is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Sport   | climbing | rugby   | rowing  | cycling  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Pet   | mouse | cat | pony | guinea-pig |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

