.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, juice
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, oliveros, ritmeester
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the ritmeester-smoker and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | juice | mirinda    | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk    |
| Cigar   | vegafina      | swisher  | ritmeester  | oliveros |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

