.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, mirinda, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
House: townhouse, art-deco, futuristic, colonial
1. the paramedic is the art-deco house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the lawyer is the person drinking water##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking water##2
9. the person drinking mirinda is between the person eating lemon and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Beverage       | sprite   | soy-milk   | mirinda | water |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| House   | futuristic    | art-deco | townhouse  | colonial    |

