.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, subway, ship, van
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, may, october
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the car##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person driving the subway is between the owner of the bird and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Transport           | car  | van | subway     | ship |
| Birthday   | october | january  | may | december       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

