.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
City: berlin, miami, marseilles, colone
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, blend, aristoff, oliveros
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the aristoff-smoker is the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the blend-smoker is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| City          | miami         | marseilles         | berlin     | colone      |
| Cigar           | aristoff | oliveros | baccarat    | blend     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

