.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, green, white, pink
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, whist, bridge
1. the fan of folk is between the person playing bridge and the fan of jazz##2
2. the freelancer is between the fan of folk and the person who likes pink##2
3. the person who likes white is between the person playing backgammon and the person who likes green##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who likes white is the person who likes white##1
6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person playing whist##1
7. the person who likes green is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Color   | pink   | green      | white   | yellow   |
| Game         | whist   | bridge    | scrabble | backgammon   |

