 2. the person eating lettuce is the person who likes azure##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person who likes azure and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person who likes ebony is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person who likes azure is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | plum | lettuce | orange  | broccoli  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Color   | ebony   | azure   | apricot | light-blue |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

