.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, go, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, iced-tea, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the person eating lettuce is the person playing go##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person playing go is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing whist is between the person playing poker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Game           | poker | whist | scrabble   | go |
| Beverage   | iced-tea         | juice       | mirinda      | sprite     |
| Sport         | parkour       | volleyball | cycling    | handball  |

