The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the tram##2
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Flower   | iris    | aconite    | azalea      | amaryllis |
| Transport       | jet-ski        | snowmobile       | tram       | airplane     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

